				<td colspan="2"><span>The person who said lvl aggro is most likely right, maybe not in the cut and dried sense, but there are a lot of modifiers to aggro. Generally, we don't generate much aggro so it isn't fair to judge the class on that, try not to get frustrated. PC is kinda wierd like that anyways, because the level range can be so large. 
<br />
Keep at it, you'll love it, trust me. Do yourself a huge favor, leave PC and go to Unrest, you'll also love it there. 
<br />
