				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Aggro Management<a name="45935"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 14 04 3:17 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Reilna's right. The higher level you get the less problems you'll have with agro. 
<br />

<br />
If it's any consolation, I had the same problem in PC until a friend of mine pointed out how to manage it. What you need to do is stop singing while the mobs are incoming. Pulse a single Anthem so it's on the group, then stop singing and back off until the tanks have solid agro. Once they've pounded on the mobs for a few seconds, start twisting again and jump in with melee.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
